F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-215_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"5e1736fd-6a46-425f-96e3-3460f9fcb4f7","comments":[],"created_at":1783786913271891001,"creation_channel":"unknown","deps":[{"link_uuid":"ff423bda-8e6e-4e10-94e7-f1bb9deecd6f","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"df83-e54d-1637-47ae"}],"description":"## Why\n\n`fsck` Check 3 (`src/rebar/_commands/fsck.py:148-171`) reclaims a stale git `index.lock` with the SAME time-of-check-to-time-of-use race that story df83 (sundried-bonny-sloth) just hardened in `gitutil._reclaim_if_stale_index_lock`: it reads `os.path.getmtime(lock_file)`, judges stale, then unconditionally `os.remove(lock_file)`. A peer can remove the stale lock and drop a fresh LIVE lock at the same path in that window, and fsck then unlinks the peer's live lock — corrupting the peer's index.\n\n## What\n\nMirror the df83 hardening: re-validate device+inode+age immediately before the unlink; abort on inode-change or refreshed mtime. Consider extracting the now-hardened reclaim helper from `gitutil` and reusing it here so the two paths cannot drift again.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] fsck Check 3 re-checks file identity (device+inode) and age at the moment of removal; mismatch aborts the unlink.\n- [ ] A deterministic inode-replacement-during-reclaim regression test covers the fsck path (or the shared helper it now calls).\n- [ ] Existing fsck stale-lock behavior (stationary stale lock removed; young lock left) still passes.\n- [ ] `make lint && make typecheck && make test` green.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"14a4cd76-49df-4919-9e36-1edd47fef32d","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"4c6c-cc0a-2d59-49ea","ticket_type":"bug","title":"Harden fsck Check 3 stale index.lock reclaim against the same TOCTOU as df83","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["52742396-45fa-4764-8e49-d669ade58cff","ff423bda-8e6e-4e10-94e7-f1bb9deecd6f","14a4cd76-49df-4919-9e36-1edd47fef32d","daf6b86a-274c-47fa-aa6c-26967fddc6c3","4fac6cbc-e333-4596-8b51-d71c1ba9dd0d"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784487885462747828,"uuid":"49d84be5-68a0-450d-9cb9-1ba1295482e0"}